# Git Shortcuts

* ggl         - git pull
* grhh        - git reset HEAD --hard
* gc          - git commit -v
* gca         - git commit -v -a
* gaa         - git add --all
* gsb         - git status -sb
* gss         - git status -s
* glog        - git log --oneline --decorate --graph
* glol        - pretty git log
* gdis        - discard local changes
* glcd        - git clone --recursive & cd
* gsync       - syncs a fork with the upstream repo using a python script
* git recall  - git recall -d 5 -a "all" (https://github.com/Fakerr/git-recall)
